long_description: gulfwater is based in new orleans, louisiana and is made up of national and international engineers, designers, and financial specialists. cities are where our dreams and ambitions become tangible. but cities also provide us with the challenges that come from urban structures and real estate competing with our natural habitat. at gulfwater we believe that by having a deep understanding of the natural forces that shape our world and working with these forces, not against them, we can help create stronger and more resilient cities and communities. gulfwater grou p llc specializes in urban stormwater management and flood mitigation. our renown specialists have earned a reputation all over the world based on their expertise and their ability to think outside of the box in building sustainable and resilient cities and urban areas. gulfwater group offers that expertise and seeks to pass it on to cities and urban areas in search of sustainable and resilient solutions to environmental challenges.
